Usage: verify_stacked_die [-help] [-check_type <typeName>]
                          [-chip_name <dieName>]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-check_type <typeName>                # check constrain types, { die_edge
                                      # bump_keepout } (string, optional)
-chip_name <dieName>                  # chip names, { dieName1 dieName2 ...}
                                      # (string, optional)